{"product_id":"mukhallat-saalim-attar-roll-on-6ml-al-saalim-perfumers-alcohol-free","title":"Mukhallat Saalim Attar (Roll On 6ml) | Al-Saalim Perfumers | Alcohol Free","description":"\u003cp\u003e  Experience the richness of tradition with Mukhallat Saalim Attar by Al-Saalim Perfumers.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis attar is a beautifully balanced blend of woody, sweet, and oriental notes, crafted for those who appreciate depth and elegance in fragrance.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMukhallat Saalim offers a warm and luxurious aroma that feels refined, long-lasting, and comforting. It is perfect for daily wear, prayer, special occasions, and evening use. The alcohol-free formulation makes it gentle on the skin and suitable for regular application.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eKey Features\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFragrance Type: Woody, Sweet \u0026amp; Oriental\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eQuantity: 6 ml Roll On\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAlcohol Free\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLong Lasting \u0026amp; Rich Aroma\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePremium glass roll-on bottle\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSuitable for men \u0026amp; women\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhy Choose Mukhallat Saalim\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTraditional mukhallat blend with a modern touch\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDeep, elegant fragrance that lasts for hours\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSmooth, non-irritating and skin-friendly\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePremium packaging, ideal for gifting\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHow to Use\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eApply lightly on pulse points such as the neck, wrists, or behind the ears for a lasting and pleasant fragrance.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"AL-SAALIM PERFUMES","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50472867627255,"sku":null,"price":179.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0923\/0755\/4551\/files\/5A8AE2AD-1122-407E-964E-A9F99F57A8FC.png?v=1777870289","url":"https